::: HELL BEAST looks to Double Punch and nods for him to back off. They all 
watched as Zardus disappeared until next monday. :::

::: GREMLIN ::: If you ask me, I wouldnt trust him. He will try to manipulate 
us!

::: HELL BEAST ::: We out number his fraction....If anyone will be 
manipulating another fraction, it will be us. Get inside. we have work for 
the battle.

~~~~~~~~~~

::: MEGATRON drops Quickstrike into the boat, the former speeder, and signals 
for the others to enter. Lugging the speeder here was hard, but now they had 
to sail it down a subterranian stream in the pitch black. :::

::: RAT TRAP took the helm, and turned on the headlights and scanners. 
MEGATRON settled into the command station. :::

::: MEGATRON ::: Come, we havent much ti-

::: RAT TRAP ::: hey! Were being followed by two Predacon signitures...

::: MEGATRON ::: What?! Who?!

::: RAT TRAP ::: Um, I think Bright Blade and Gangon....but i could be wrong.

::: MEGATRON ::: Pray that you are not rodent. I dont think they are worth 
our time. Lets go.

::: The speeder humms as it takes off into the stream :::

~~~~~~~~~~`

::: TRANSANULAS parks outside the Maximal base. He looks to the blast doors 
and raises his comm unit ::: Liono Prime! This is TRANSANULAS, i wish to join 
you, and the Maximals.

::: His Predacon signiture changes to the Maximal symbol :::
